### 3Ô∏è‚É£ Nobody Owns the Alert

When an alert fires:

- Security assumes it‚Äôs IT  
- IT assumes it‚Äôs DevOps  
- DevOps assumes it‚Äôs ‚Äúexpected behavior‚Äù  

So nothing happens.

Zero Trust becomes **Zero Responsibility**.

