### 4Ô∏è‚É£ Detection Without Response Is Theater

Even when something is noticed:

- No authority to disable accounts  
- No confidence to kill sessions  
- No playbooks that won‚Äôt cause outages  

So teams ‚Äúmonitor‚Äù the attacker.  
Politely. Like wildlife photography.

